title: Softbank will succeed even if its WeWork investment doesn’t work out - Ep 8
itunes:title: Softbank will succeed even if its WeWork investment doesn’t work out - Ep 8
description:
Is SoftBank setting itself up for failure by investing in WeWork? Despite his apprehension regarding WeWork, Vitaliy isn't worried. Hear his take on it & the reasoning behind his investing firm's decision to hold SoftBank stock.

You can read this article online at https://contrarianedge.com/softbank-will-succeed-even-if-its-wework-investment-doesnt-work-out/

Disclosure: Read this before you buy your next stock
